  "Description": {
    "English": "A heavy, oozing slime. It is moving gently, as if it has a heartbeat of its own.<br><br>Nutrient source: <span class=\"name name-fuel\">unknown</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种渗出的浓稠黏液。它缓慢地移动，仿佛里面有一颗跳动的心。<br><br>营养源：<span class=\"name name-fuel\">未知</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种渗出的浓稠黏液。它缓慢地移动，仿佛里面有一颗跳动的心。<br><br>营养源：<span class=\"name name-fuel\">未知</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一團笨重黏呼呼的軟泥。會緩慢移動，彷彿有自己的心跳。<br><br>養分來源：<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不明</span>。"
  },
